#

Honey Garlic Pork Bites

25 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Soy

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyQuickSavory

Description

Succulent bites of pork glazed in a sweet and savory honey garlic sauce, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • pork tenderloin: 1 pound
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • ginger: 1 teaspoon, grated
  • vegetable oil: 2 tablespoons
  • sesame seeds: 1 tablespoon (optional)
